  "description": "Technical comparison of mid-range portable HEPA air purifiers in the US market ($80-200, 200-400 sq ft coverage class). Covers the Levoit Core 300, Winix 5500-2, Coway AP-1512HH Mighty, Blueair Blue Pure 411, and Honeywell HPA200. Evaluates filtration class, CADR, noise, power, filter cost, smart features, and certifications against standards rather than marketing.",
